%3Binappropriate%26quot%3B%20gifts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPost%20the%20backlash%2C%20the%20Murmansk%20regional%20branch%20of%20United%20Russia%20shared%20a%20video%20of%20one%20of%20the%20mothers%20of%20killed%20soldiers%20thanking%20them%20for%20the%20meat%20grinder.%C2%A0Calling%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Btimely%26quot%3B%20gift%2C%20the%20woman%20said%20she%20%26quot%3Bwanted%20to%20buy%26quot%3B%20the%20meat%20grinder%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20asked%20you%20for%20it%2C%20in%20principle.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meat%20grinder%2C%20which%20one%20soldier's%20mother%20received%2C%20was%20not%20%26quot%3Bpart%20of%20the%20standard%20set%2C%20but%20the%20woman%20requested%20it%2C%20and%20of%20course%2C%20we%20couldn't%20refuse%2C%26quot%3B%20Russian%20news%20outlet%20Meduza%20quoted%C2%A0Mayor%20Maxim%20Chengayev%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20party%20added%20the%20gesture%20was%20being%20misrepresented%2C%20urging%20all%20to%20not%20support%20%26quot%3Binhumane%20and%20provocative%20interpretations.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20days%20after%20billionaire%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20special%20advisor%20to%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20accused%20%26quot%3Bevil%26quot%3B%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20of%20prolonging%20the%20war%20with%20Russia.%20The%20world's%20richest%20person%20called%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bnever-ending%20graft%20meat%20grinder.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BZelensky%20wants%20a%20forever%20war%2C%20a%20never-ending%20graft%20meat%20grinder.%20This%20is%20evil%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Musk%20wrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EZelensky%20wants%20a%20forever%20war%2C%20a%20never-ending%20graft%20meat%20grinder.%20This%20is%20evil.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FFVaEkIm7Gq%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FFVaEkIm7Gq%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Elon%20Musk%20(%40elonmusk)%2