0rights%20of%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BNo%20ideology%20justifies%20the%20dispossession%20of%20a%20people%20or%20the%20denial%20of%20their%20right%20to%20self-determination.%20%26quot%3BCanada%20has%20legal%20obligations%20to%20support%2C%20not%20obstruct%2C%20Palestinian%20self-determination-failure%20to%20do%20so%20can%20have%20legal%20consequences%20under%20international%20law.%20Canadians%20should%20be%20fully%20aware%20of%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20speech%20sparked%20a%20row%20on%20social%20media%2C%20with%20an%20X%20user%20saying%20%26quot%3BHe%20might%20as%20well%20declare%20himself%20proud%20of%20apartheid%20laws%2C%20proud%20of%20Israel's%20illegal%20occupation%2C%20proud%20of%20their%20genocide.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20social%20media%20user%20wrote%20that%20this%20remark%20in%20his%20last%20days%20in%20office%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Bhis%20legacy%26quot%3B%2C%20while%20another%20said%20%26quot%3BNo%20comment%2C%20only%20nausea%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Trudeau%20had%20said%20that%20Zionism%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20a%20dirty%20word%26quot%3B%2C%20while%20calling%20for%20a%20two-state%20solution%20to%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20to%20ensure%20%26quot%3Bcomprehensive%2C%20just%20and%20lasting%20peace%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrudeau's%20statement%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20he%20is%20set%20to%20be%20replaced%20as%20the%20Liberal%20Party%20will%20elect%20a%20leader%20to%20replace%20him.%20Trudeau%2C%20who%20became%20Liberal%20leader%20in%202013%20before%20taking%20over%20as%20prime%20minister%20two%20years%20later%2C%20announced%20in%20early%20January%20that%20he%20planned%20to%20resign%2C%20overcome%20by%20dismal%20polling%20numbers%20and%20internal%20party%20dissent.%20The%20front-runner%20is%20Mark%20Carney%2C%20who%20led%20the%20Bank%20of%20Canada%20before%20becoming%20the%20first%20non-Briton%20to%20serve%20as%20governor%20of%20the%20Bank%20of%20England.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C