als%2Famp_articleshow%2F118797181.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCan't%20Accept%2C%20It's%20Unsafe%26quot%3B%3A%20Christian%20Michel%20On%20Bail%20In%20AgustaWestland%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChristian%20Michel%20James%2C%20an%20alleged%20middleman%20in%20AgustaWestland%20case%2C%20on%20Friday%20offered%20to%20%26quot%3Bfinish%20his%20sentence%26quot%3B%20and%20leave%20India%20instead%20of%20walking%20out%20on%20bail%20owing%20to%20%26quot%3Bsecurity%20risks%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJames%20was%20addressing%20special%20judge%20Sanjeev%20Aggarwal%20when%20he%20made%20the%20plea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20reprieve%20in%20the%20CBI%20and%20ED%20cases%20against%20him%2C%20the%20special%20court%20imposed%20the%20necessary%20bail%20conditions%20for%20releasing%20him%20on%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20on%20March%204%20granted%20him%20bail%20in%20the%20ED%20case%20and%20directed%20for%20saddling%20Michel%20with%20the%20necessary%20bail%20riders%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20February%2018%20granted%20the%20relief%20in%20the%20CBI%20case%20subject%20to%20the%20trial%20court's%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20the%20judge%20asked%20James%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20are%20you%20now%3F%20God%20has%20been%20kind%20to%20you%20in%20the%20last%20two%20months.%20You%20have%20got%20bail%20in%20both%20cases.%26quot%3B%20James%2C%20however%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BDelhi%20is%20just%20a%20larger%20prison.%20My%20family%20cannot%20come%20to%20me...My%20security%20is%20at%20risk.%20I%20would%20rather%20complete%20my%20sentence%20and%20leave%20the%20country.%26quot%3B%20The%20judge%20asked%20Michel%20how%20could%20he%20continue%20to%20be%20incarcerated%20when%20bail%20had%20been%20granted%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20cannot%20accept%20the%20bail.%20It's%20unsafe.%20Every%20time%20I%20step%20out%20of%20Tihar%20(prison)%2C%20something%20happens%2C%26quot%3B%20Michel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20aspect%20of%20furnishing%20a%20surety%20bond%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20can%20a%20person%20who%20has%20been%20in%20jail%20for%20six%20years%20produce%20local%20sureties%3F%26quot%3B%20After%20Michel%20stressed%20he%20did%20not%20want%20to%20be%20released%20on%20bail%20because%20of%20security%20reasons%2C%20the%20judge%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BCan't%20you%20find%20a%20safehouse%20in%20Delhi%3F%26quot%3B%20Michel%20then%20offered%20to%20%26quot%3Bnarrate%20in%20private%20the%20incident%26quot%3B%20he%20faced%20when%20he%20was%20admitted%20to%20AIIMS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20problem%20I%20have%20is%20with%20the%20police.%20I%20would%20rather%20talk%20to%20you%20in%20private%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20then%20asked%20the%20media%20persons%20and%20the%20police%20personnel%20to%20wait%20outside%20for%20some%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20around%204.30%20pm%2C%20the%20court%20passed%20its%20order%2C%20laying%20down%20the%20conditions%20for%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conditions%20include%20James%20marking%20his%20attendance%20physically%20before%20the%20investigating%20officers%20once%20every%2015%20days%2C%20providing%20his%20cellphone%20number%2C%20email%20and%20residential%20address%20to%20the%20probe%20agencies%20aside%20from%20not%20leaving%20the%20country%20without%20the%20court's%20permission%20and%20not%20tampering%20with%20the%20evidence%20or%20attempting%20to%20influence%20the%20witnesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20accused%20shall%20not%20interact%20with%20respect%20to%20the%20present%20case%20with%20the%20media%20nor%20shall%20communicate%20regarding%20this%20case%20at%20any%20forum%2C%20during%20the%20trial%20of%20this%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court's%20order%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20directed%20James%20to%20furnish%20a%20personal%20bond%20and%20surety%20of%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20in%20both%20cases%20and%20surrender%20his%20passport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E