3Cp%3EWith%20the%20temperatures%20rapidly%20rising%20in%20Dubai%2C%20spin%20bowling%20is%20set%20to%20be%20become%20even%20more%20important%20to%20the%20teams'%20plans%20for%20the%20final.%20The%20center-wicket%20has%20been%20under%20the%20covers%20over%20the%20last%20few%20days.%20The%20first%20look%20of%20the%20wicket%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20made%20public%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741400100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fjsodgle_dubai-venue-x_625x300_07_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Findia-vs-new-zealand-champions-trophy-pitch-selected-heres-its-pakistan-connection-7871919%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20pitch%20for%20the%20India%20vs%20New%20Zealand%20final%20in%20the%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%20has%20been%20selected.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Ireland's%20politicians%20say%20St%20Patrick's%20Washington%20trip%20makes%20a%20difference%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741399731000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F35f9%2Flive%2Fd366e050-fb43-11ef-9e61-71ee71f26eb1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc17qnxrq1y7o%232%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Politicians%20from%20the%20island%20of%20Ireland%20are%20visiting%20Washington%20DC%20this%20week%20-%20but%20it's%20not%20without%20controversy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A28%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc17qnxrq1y7o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc17qnxrq1y7o.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc17qnxrq1y7o.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vladimir%20Putin%20Ready%20For%20Ukraine%20Truce%20Talks.%20But%20There%20Are%20Conditions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump%20kept%20up%20the%20pressure%20on%20Ukraine%20to%20move%20ahead%20with%20a%20peace%20deal%20as%20signals%20emerged%20that%20the%20Kremlin%20would%20be%20willing%20to%20accept%20a%20temporary%20truce%20under%20certain%20conditions.%C2%A0As%20the%20American%20president%20pursues%20an%20agreement%20to%20end%20the%20war%20triggered%20by%20Russia's%20full-scale%20invasion%20of%20its%20neighbor%20three%20years%20ago%2C%20he's%20reversed%20years%20of%20US%20support%20for%20Kyiv%2C%20instead%20courting%20Moscow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20doing%20very%20well%20with%20Russia%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20told%20reporters%20in%20the%20Oval%20Office%20on%20Friday.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20finding%20it%20more%20difficult%2C%20frankly%2C%20to%20deal%20with%20Ukraine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20advisers%20are%20already%20sketching%20out%20how%20they%20might%20ease%20the%20sanctions%20imposed%20on%20Russia%20because%20of%20the%20war%2C%20including%20a%20cap%20imposed%20on%20prices%20for%20its%20oil%20sales%2C%20according%20to%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20discussions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20US%20and%20Ukrainian%20officials%20are%20preparing%20to%20meet%20Tuesday%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20improve%20relations%20and%20restore%20American%20arms%20and%20intelligence%20to%20Kyiv%2C%20both%20of%20which%20Trump%20suspended%20after%20a%20White%20House%20blowup%20with%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskiy%20on%20Feb.%2028.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20embrace%20of%20Russia%20has%20raised%20fears%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20among%20its%20allies%20in%20Europe%20that%20he%20would%20try%20to%20force%20Kyiv%20into%20a%20deal%20on%20terms%20favorable%20to%20the%20Kremlin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussian%20officials%20conveyed%20their%20willingness%20to%20consider%20a%20short-term%20truce%2C%20provided%20there%20was%20progress%20toward%20a%20final%20peace%20settlement%2C%20in%20talks%20with%20US%20counterparts%20last%20month%2C%20according%20to%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20who%20asked%20for%20anonymity%20to%20describe%20private%20talks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20agree%20to%20a%20cessation%20of%20hostilities%2C%20there%20would%20have%20to%20be%20a%20clear%20understanding%20about%20the%20framework%20principles%20of%20the%20final%20peace%20accord%2C%20two%20people%20with%20knowledge%20of%20the%20matter%20said.%20Russia%20will%20insist%20in%20particular%20on%20establishing%20the%20parameters%20of%20an%20eventual%20peacekeeping%20mission%2C%20including%20agreement%20on%20which%20countries%20would%20take%20part%2C%20said%20another%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKremlin%20spokesman%20Dmitry%20Peskov%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20stepped%20up%20air%20attacks%20on%20Ukraine%20overnight%2C%20officials%20in%20Kyiv%20said%2C%20launching%20hundreds%20of%20missiles%2C%20drones%20and%20other%20weapons%20at%20targets%20across%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%20Trump%20said%20he's%20confident%20Vladimir%20Putin%20wants%20an%20accord.%20But%20early%20Friday%2C%20he%20threatened%20in%20a%20social-media%20post%20to%20impose%20more%20sanctions%20and%20tariffs%20on%20Russia%20if%20it%20doesn't%20move%20forward%20with%20talks.%20He%20didn't%20mention%20those%20threats%20in%20his%20comments%20later%20and%20it%20wasn't%20clear%20what%20new%20restrictions%20could%20be%20imposed%20given%20the%20broad%20limits%20already%20in%20place%20on%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20his%20January%2020%20inauguration%2C%20Trump%20has%20overturned%20US%20policy%20on%20Russia's%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20to%20try%20to%20bring%20a%20rapid%20end%20to%20Europe's%20worst%20conflict%20in%2080%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20held%20telephone%20talks%20with%20Putin%20last%20month%20and%20they%20agreed%20to%20hold%20a%20summit%2C%20though%20no%20date%20has%20been%20set.%20Trump%20abandoned%20US%20support%20for%20Ukraine's%20eventual%20entry%20into%20NATO%2C%20and%20his%20top%20officials%20said%20it%20was%20unrealistic%20to%20expect%20a%20return%20of%20all%20Ukrainian%20territory%20seized%20by%20Russia%20since%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20confrontation%20with%20Zelenskiy%20at%20the%20White%20House%2C%20Trump%20paused%20military%20aid%20to%20Ukraine%20and%20has%20suspended%20some%20intelligence-sharing%20with%20Kyiv%2C%20shocking%20European%20allies%20who%20say%20the%20US%20risks%20rewarding%20Russia's%20aggression.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20on%20Friday%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20National%20Geospatial-Intelligence%20Agency%20said%20it%20had%20temporarily%20halted%20Ukraine's%20access%20to%20satellite%20imagery%20from%20the%20Global%20Enhanced%20GEOINT%20Delivery%20system.%20The%20suspension%20was%20reported%20earlier%20by%20the%20New%20York%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20nightly%20video%20address%2C%20Zelenskiy%20cited%20the%20latest%20Russian%20attacks%20as%20evidence%20that%20the%20Kremlin%20%26quot%3Bhas%20to%20be%20forced%20into%20peace.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20took%20a%20conciliatory%20note%20with%20Trump%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BToday%20the%20most%20intensive%20work%20with%20President%20Trump's%20team%20ever%20has%20been%20going%20on%20all%20day%20at%20various%20levels.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUkraine%20is%20very%20constructive%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZelenskiy%20is%20sending%20top%20aides%20to%20meet%20with%20Trump%20administration%20officials%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia%20on%20Tuesday.%20US%20special%20envoy%20Steve%20Witkoff%20said%20the%20meeting%20was%20intended%20to%20reach%20%26quot%3Ba%20framework%20for%20a%20peace%20agreement%20and%20an%20initial%20ceasefire.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%20said%20it%20won't%20accept%20the%20presence%20of%2