20off-road%20means%20such%20as%20agriculture%20or%20mining.%20The%20vehicles%20ferry%20not%20only%20students%2C%20but%20anyone%20who%20enters%20the%20institute's%20campus%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Rajalakshmi%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20four-wheeler%20electric%20vehicles%20were%20developed%20by%20the%20engineers%20at%20TiHAN%2C%20a%20technology%20innovation%20hub%20founded%20by%20IIT-Hyderabad%20and%20sanctioned%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20Science%20and%20Technology%20under%20the%20National%20Mission%20on%20Interdisciplinary%20Cyber-Physical%20Systems.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20vehicle%20consists%20of%20a%20screen%20that%20shows%20the%20route%20as%20it%20gets%20signals%20from%20the%20vehicle%20sensors%20for%20various%20indications%20such%20as%20a%203D%20map%20for%20navigation%20or%20an%20obstacle%20on%20the%20way.%20It%20stops%20at%20every%20bus%20stop%20for%2010%20seconds.%20Announcements%20related%20to%20onboarding%20and%20alighting%20from%20the%20vehicle%20are%20also%20made%20through%20the%20screens%20and%20voice%20for%20the%20passengers.%20The%20vehicles%20are%20also%20equipped%20with%20an%20emergency%20button%20to%20stop%20it%20in%20case%20a%20situation%20arises.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20software%20and%20hardware%20components%20have%20been%20built%20by%20the%20institute.%20The%20one-of-a-kind%20project%20for%20India%2C%20the%20TiHAN%20project%2C%20is%20worth%20Rs%20132%20crore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shuttle%20services%20on%20the%20driverless%20vehicle%20are%20offered%20six%20times%20a%20day%20-%20three%20each%20in%20the%20morning%20and%20afternoon.%20While%20one%20of%20the%20shuttle%20has%20a%20seating%20capacity%20of%2014%20people%2C%20the%20other%20is%20smaller%20and%20can%20accommodate%20only%20six%20people.%20Ms%20Rajalakshmi%20says%20the%20test%20vehicle%20has%20run%20for%20over%2015%2C000%20kilometres%20ferrying%20over%2010%2C000%20people%20inside%20the%20IIT%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20possi