%20buy%20their%20first%20rental%20property%20in%20cash.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENow%20they%20own%20five%20rentals%20that%20bring%20in%20%2428%2C000%20a%20year%20in%20passive%20income.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMarried%20couple%20Marques%20and%20Shyra%2C%20who%20blog%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.blackmarrieddebtfree.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBlack%2C%20Married%20%26amp%3B%20Debt%20Free%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20don't%20disclose%20their%20last%20name%20online%2C%20have%20been%20building%20a%20portfolio%20of%20rental%20properties%20since%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20starting%20their%20debt-payoff%20journey%2C%20which%20began%20in%202015%20and%20included%20crushing%20%2433%2C000%20of%20credit%20and%20student%20loan%20debt%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20mortgage%20on%20their%20home%20near%20Sacramento%2C%20California%2C%20the%20couple%20decided%20their%20next%20big-ticket%20goal%20would%20be%20investing%20in%20rental%20properties.%20They%20spoke%20to%20Business%20Insider%20about%20their%20investment%20strategy%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey've%20amassed%20five%20rentals%2C%20which%20rake%20in%20%2428%2C000%20a%20year%20in%20passive%20income%20after%20expenses.%20However%2C%20to%20pay%20for%20their%20first%20rental%20property%2C%20they%20decided%20on%20an%20out-of-box%20approach%3A%20tapping%20into%20the%20equity%20in%20their%20Sacramento%20condo%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fbuying-home-cash-vs-mortgage%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuy%20the%20home%20in%20cash%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ef3ac6b9-d50f-41c6-8add-c208cbfbc0ba%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThey%20used%20a%20HELOC%20to%20purchase%20the%20rental%20property%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20Marques%20and%20Shyra%20knocked%20down%20their%20debt%2C%20they%20saw%20real%20estate%20as%20a%20path%20to%20financial%20freedom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20though%20we%20were%20debt-free%2C%20which%20impacted%20our%20quality%20of%20life%2C%20the%20next%20day%2C%20we%20were%20stuck%20in%20traffic%20going%20to%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Marques.%20%26quot%3BIt%20didn't%20lower%20our%20stress%20level%2C%20and%20we%20didn't%20achieve%20financial%20freedom.%20We%20wanted%20more%20freedom%20with%20our%20time%20and%20choices.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWhile%20the%20couple%20could've%20saved%20for%20a%20down%20payment%20for%20their%20rental%20property%2C%20it%20would've%20taken%20months%2C%20if%20not%20a%20few%20years.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EAfter%20doing%20their%20homework%20and%20mulling%20over%20different%20options%2C%20Marques%20and%20Shyra%20decided%20to%20tap%20into%20their%20primary%20home's%20equity%20to%20buy%20their%20first%20rental%20property%20entirely%20in%20cash%20using%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fcurrent-heloc-rates%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehome%20equity%20line%20of%20credit%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20borrowed%20%24120%2C000%20at%20a%20rate%20of%205.5%25%3B%20it%20was%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20felt%20that%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fheloc-pros-and-cons%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHELOC%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20give%20us%20leverage%20and%20negotiation%20power%20that%20traditional%20financing%20would%20not%20provide%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Shyra.%20%26quot%3BWe%20would%20get%20a%20better%20deal%20and%20higher%20cash%20flow.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20HELOC%20is%20a%20revolving%20line%20of%20credit%2C%20and%20is%20backed%20up%20by%20your%20home%2C%20which%20serves%20as%20collateral.%20HELOCs%20can%20be%20used%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20things%2C%20such%20as%20funding%20home%20improvement%20projects%2C%20consolidating%20debt%2C%20footing%20the%20bill%20for%20higher%20education%2C%20or%20paying%20for%20medical%20bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilar%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fbest-credit-cards%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecredit%20card%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20you%20can%20take%20out%20different%20amounts%20and%20are%20responsible%20for%20paying%20off%20the%20balance.%20HELOCS%20also%20typically%20have%20a%20draw%20period%2C%20which%20is%20a%20set%20amount%20of%20time%20that%20you%20can%20tap%20into%20your%20credit%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2275a1e251-fc36-4eb4-86ea-107ab8cd33bf%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThey%20were%20able%20to%20close%20on%20the%20process%20quickly%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20couple%20obtained%20the%20HELOC%2C%20which%20took%20about%2030%20days%2C%20it%20took%20about%20two%20weeks%20to%20complete%20the%20second%20major%20transaction%2C%20the%20rental%20home%20purchase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20we%20used%20a%20HELOC%2C%20we%20had%20access%20to%20a%20form%20of%20cash%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Shyra.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20as%20more%20sellers%20are%20looking%20for%20cash%20buyers%2C%20the%20closing%20process%20went%20by%20quickly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20top%20of%20a%20quick%20close%2C%20buying%20in%20cash%20got%20them%20a%20better%20purchase%20price.%20While%20the%20three-bedroom%2C%20one-and-half-bath%20home%20in%20a%20suburb%20in%20Greensboro%2C%20North%20Carolina%2C%20was%20listed%20for%20%24110%2C000%2C%20the%20couple%20put%20on%20their%20negotiation%20hats%20and%20managed%20to%20get%20it%20down%20to%20%24104%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCompared%20to%20a%20conventional%20loan%2C%20time%20is%20working%20in%20your%20favor%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Shyra%2C%20explaining%20that%20the%20time%20it%20takes%20to%20underwrite%20a%20traditional%20mortgage%20could%20have%20slowed%20down%20the%20deal.%20With%20the%20cash%20from%20the%20HELOC%2C%20the%20home%20purchase%20was%20just%20between%20the%20seller%20and%20the%20couple.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228384b269-db03-468c-9fc4-7f67d2a03ebc%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThey%20prioritized%20making%20a%20profit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20avoid%20getting%20swept%20up%20in%20the%20allure%20of%20a%20particular%20rental%20property%2C%20Marques%20and%20Shyra%20focused%20on%20making%20sure%20their%20rental%20income%20covered%20both%20their%20monthly%20HELOC%20payment%20%E2%80%94%20about%20%24700%20%E2%80%94%20along%20with%20any%20additional%20expenses%20of%20homeownership.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20pay%20it%20back%20%E2%80%94%20with%20interest%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Marques%20of%20the%20HELOC.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20a%20gift.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20choosing%20the%20location%20for%20their%20rental%20property%2C%20they%20looked%20for%20a%20turnkey%20home%20that%20was%20pretty%20much%20move-in%20ready%20for%20tenants.%20They%20live%20out%20of%20state%2C%20so%20they%20didn't%20want%20to%20oversee%20major%20projects%20from%20afar.%20Another%20criteria%3F%20Homes%20outside%20of%20major%20cities%20that%20were%20in%20growing%20areas%20with%20thriving%20economies%20and%20booming%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELastly%2C%20the%20pair%20made%20sure%20to%20land%20on%20a%20HELOC%20with%20a%20fixed%20interest%20rate%20versus%20an%20adjustable%20rate.%20That%20way%2C%20the%20HELOC%20payments%20wouldn't%20fluctuate.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20buying%20a%20rental%20property%2C%20you%20can't%20go%20up%20and%20down%20in%20your%20rent%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Marques.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e2d33fec-19e6-476e-94ae-0f3d4b0bd1d8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThey%20have%20a%20reliable%20out-of-state%20team%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%2C%20who%20eventually%20grew%20their%20portfolio%20to%20three%20properties%20in%20North%20Carolina%20and%20two%20in%20Alabama%2C%20made%20a%20point%20to%20build%20a%20trustworthy%2C%20experienced%20team%20to%20manage%20their%20properties.%20This%20team%20consisted%20of%20a%20property%20manager%2C%20lender%2C%20real%20estate%20agent%2C%20and%20a%20general%20contractor%20to%20oversee%20all%20maintenance%20and%20repairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHaving%20a%20team%20in%20place%20gives%20us%20peace%20of%20mind%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Marques.%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20worry%20about%20our%20properties%2C%20and%20have%20confidence%20that%20our%20tenants'%20needs%20are%20being%20met%20as%20well%20as%20the%20needs%20of%20our%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20perk%20of%20having%20a%20solid%20team%20to%20take%20care%20of%20their%20rental%20properties%20was%20that%20the%20couple%20rarely%20needed%20to%20travel%20for%20in-person%20visits.%20However%2C%20they%20did%20make%20it%20a%20point%20to%20see%20every%20property%20they%20bought%20before%20they%20handed%20over%20the%20keys%20to%20the%20property%20manager.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2256e31fb4-02f3-46f8-9fbd-56920911b4e5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThey%20used%20'extra'%20money%20from%20the%20HELOC%20to%20buy%20their%20second%20rental%20property%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20couple%20took%20out%20a%20%24120%2C000%20HELOC%20on%20a%20home%20with%20a%20%24104%2C000%20price%20tag%2C%20they%20intended%20to%20keep%20the%20remaining%20%2416%2C000%20untouched%20for%20maintenance%20and%20repairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20they%20ended%20up%20not%20needing%20to%20tap%20into%20the%20remainder%20of%20their%20HELOC%2C%20so%20they%20used%20it%20toward%20a%20down%20payment%20on%20a%20second%20rental%20property%2C%20which%20they%20bought%20using%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fconventional-mortgage%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econventional%20mortgage%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20beauty%20of%20a%20HELOC%20is%20you%20can%20make%20different%20transactions%20with%20the%20same%20line%20of%20credit%2C%20explained%20Marques.%20For%20instance%2C%20if%20you%20take%20out%20a%20%24100%2C000%20HELOC%2C%20you%20can%20use%20%2410%2C000%20of%20it%20now%2C%20%2410%2C000%20later%20for%20something%20else%2C%20and%20so%20forth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20in%20all%2C%20Marques%20and%20Shyra%20said%20they%20were%20happy%20they%20made%20the%20decision%20to%20purchase%20their%20first%20rental%20property%20with%20a%20HELOC.%20They%20loved%20how%20smooth%20the%20process%20was%2C%20and%20how%20buying%20a%20home%20with%20cash%20gave%20them%20leverage%20and%20more%20negotiating%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20an%20adventure%20to%20go%20across%20the%20country%20in%20a%20plane%20to%20invest%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Shyra.%20%26quot%3BWe%20do%20it%20in%20a%20way%20that%20limits%20our%20risk%20while%20receiving%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20reward.%20And%20we've%20been%20able%20to%20reap%20the%20benefits%20of%20appreciation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon't%20know%20where%20to%20start%3F%20Consider%20a%20financial%20advisor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsmartasset.com%2Fretirement%2Ffind-a-financial-planner%3Futm_source%3Dbusinessinsider%26utm_medium%3Dcpc%26utm_campaign%3Dbus__falc_bicontent%26utm_content%3DBI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EFinding%20a%20financial%20advisor%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20hard.%20SmartAsset's%20free%20tool%20matches%20you%20with%20up%20to%20three%20fiduciary%20financial%20advisors%20who%20serve%20your%20area%20in%20minutes.%20Each%20advisor%20has%20been%20vetted%20by%20SmartAsset%20and%20is%20held%20to%20a%20fiduciary%20standard%20to%20act%20in%20your%20best%20interests.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsmartasset.com%2Fretirement%2Ffind-a-financial-planner%3Futm_source%3Dbusinessinsider%26utm_medium%3Dcpc%26utm_campaign%3Dbus__falc_bicontent%26utm_content%3DBI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%20Start%20your%20search%20now.%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20published%20in%20October%202022.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C