ounced%20Friday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20pair%20had%20been%20found%20dead%20in%20their%20New%20Mexico%20home%20on%20February%2026%20under%20unusual%20circumstances.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHackman%20died%20of%20complications%20from%20heart%20disease%20about%20a%20week%20after%20Arakawa%20Hackman%20died%20of%20hantavirus.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Santa%20Fe%20County%20chief%20medical%20examiner%20said%20on%20Friday%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgene-hackman-dead-betsy-arakawa-dog-home-cause-of-death-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGene%20Hackman%20died%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20natural%20causes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2095-year-old%20Oscar-winning%20actor%2C%20his%20wife%2C%20Betsy%20Arakawa%20Hackman%2C%20and%20one%20of%20their%20dogs%20were%20found%20dead%20on%20February%2026%20at%20their%20New%20Mexico%20home.%20For%20over%20a%20week%2C%20it%20was%20unclear%20how%20they'd%20each%20died%2C%20though%20authorities%20said%20they'd%20been%20dead%20for%20quite%20some%20time%20and%20their%20deaths%20were%20%26quot%3Bsuspicious%20enough%20in%20nature%20to%20require%20a%20thorough%20search%20and%20investigation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20has%20now%20concluded.%20At%20a%20Santa%20Fe%20County%20Sheriff%20press%20conference%20on%20Friday%2C%20chief%20medical%20examiner%20Dr.%20Heather%20Jarrell%20said%20Hackman%20died%20of%20complications%20from%20heart%20disease%20and%20Alzheimer's%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArakawa%20Hackman%2C%20who%20was%2065%2C%20died%20of%20hantavirus%20pulmonary%20syndrome.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fconditions-symptoms%2Fwhat-is-hantavirus%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHantavirus%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20flu-like%20disease%20carried%20by%20infected%20rats%2C%20which%20is%20rarely%20passed%20between%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20deaths%20were%20classified%20as%20natural.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPills%20were%20previously%20reported%20to%20have%20been%20found%20on-site%3B%20Jarrell%20said%20they%20were%20prescribed%20thyroid%20medication%20and%20not%20a%20matter%20of%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJarrell%20said%20it%20was%20unprecedented%20for%20her%20office%20to%20comment%20on%20deaths%20but%20felt%20it%20was%20important%20in%20this%20case%20to%20disseminate%20accurate%20information%20and%20said%20she%20had%20spoken%20to%20Hackman's%20family%20about%20the%20autopsy%20findings%20before%20the%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArakawa%20Hackman%20collapsed%20in%20a%20bathroom%20at%20the%20couple's%20New%20Mexico%20residence%20and%20succumbed%20to%20the%20virus%20%26quot%3Bpretty%20quickly%26quot%3B%20after%20it%20had%20progressed%20enough%20that%20fluid%20began%20to%20fill%20her%20lungs%2C%20Jarrell%20said.%20The%20medical%20examiner%20added%20that%20she%20does%20not%20believe%20Arakwa%20Hackman%20was%20alive%20for%20an%20extended%20period%20after%20she%20collapsed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20Hackman's%20advanced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Falzheimers-vs-dementia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAlzheimer's%20disease%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Jarrell%20said%20it%20is%20likely%20he%20was%20home%20with%20his%20deceased%20wife%20for%20over%20a%20week%20before%20he%20died.%20She%20said%20it%20is%20unclear%20whether%20he%20knew%20she%20had%20died%20or%20if%20he%20attempted%20to%20get%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr.%20Hackman%20showed%20evidence%20of%20advanced%20Alzheimer's%20disease%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0I'm%20not%20aware%20of%20what%20his%20normal%20daily%20functioning%20capability%20was%2C%26quot%3B%20Jarrell%20said%20in%20the%20Friday%20press%20conference.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20in%20a%20very%20poor%20state%20of%20health%2C%20and%20he%20had%20significant%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fconditions-symptoms%2Fwhat-is-heart-disease%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheart%20disease%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20I%20think%20ultim