r%20some%20of%20their%20competitors%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%20for%20now.%20Many%20businesses%20that%20manufacture%20their%20goods%20in%20China%20are%20now%20paying%20extra%20in%20tariffs%2C%20while%20de%20minimis%20allows%20companies%20like%20Temu%20and%20Shein%20to%20import%20low-cost%20items%20without%20paying%20any%20kind%20of%20duty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20will%20be%20paying%20them%20except%20for%20Temu%20and%20Shein.%20(For%20now%3B%20we%20know%20de%20minimis%20is%20going%20away%20in%20the%20future%2C)%26quot%3B%20Marketplace%20Pulse%20founder%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fjuozas_temu-and-shein-advantage-over-other-retailers-activity-7302692641693921281-4y_5%3Futm_source%3Dshare%26utm_medium%3Dmember_desktop%26rcm%3DACoAAAtNuO4BwQhonnAjH8qQL8LOh0aR9YKu83g%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJuozas%20Kaziuk%C4%97nas%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20in%20a%20LinkedIn%20post.%20%26quot%3BBizarrely%2C%20Temu%20and%20Shein%20never%20had%20it%20better.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeither%20company%20responded%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20early%20February%2C%20Trump%20announced%20that%20he%20would%20simultaneously%20impose%20tariffs%20on%20Mexican%2C%20Canadian%2C%20and%20Chinese%20products%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbrands-scramble-as-trump-ends-de-minimis-shipments-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eend%20the%20de%20minimis%20exemption%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20allowed%20retailers%20to%20import%20goods%20duty-free%20as%20long%20as%20they%20were%20valued%20at%20less%20than%20%24800%20and%20being%20sent%20directly%20to%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20just%20a%20few%20days%20later%2C%20Trump%20issued%20another%20executive%20order%20that%20said%20de%20minimis%20%E2%80%94%20also%20known%20as%20Section%20321%20%E2%80%94%20would%20remain%20in%20place%20until%20customs%20officials%20could%20establish%20a%20new%20process%20for%20collecting%20duty%20on%20packages%20sent%20using%20the%20provision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%2020%25%20tariffs%20on%20Chinese%20goods%20have%20gone%20ahead.%20(Trump%20temporarily%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-mexico-tariffs-pause-usmca-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epaused%20the%2025%25%20tariffs%20on%20Mexican%20and%20Canadian%20goods%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Thursday%2C%20saying%20they%20would%20be%20on%20hold%20until%20April%202.)%20That%20means%20that%20even%20if%20an%20item%20would%20have%20been%20subject%20to%20a%20tariff%2C%20importers%20do%20not%20currently%20have%20to%20pay%20that%20tariff%20if%20they%20are%20shipped%20via%20de%20minimis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20reason%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftemu-shein-under-increased-pressure-from-us-lawmakers-de-minimis-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elawmakers%20have%20advocated%20for%20the%20repeal%20of%20de%20minimis%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20recent%20years%20is%20that%20it's%20difficult%20for%20American%20businesses%20to%20compete%20with%20companies%20using%20de%20minimis%20to%20save%20money.%20They%20also%20have%20argued%20that%20de%20minimis%20allows%20for%20the%20import%20of%20illicit%20goods%20like%20fentanyl%20%E2%80%94%20an%20argument%20that%20Trump%20has%20echoed%20in%20executive%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20we%20are%20immediately%20penalizing%20US%20businesses%20who%20manufacture%20offshore%20while%20providing%20this%20continued%20advantage%20to%20Chinese%20marketplaces%20such%20as%20Temu%20and%20Shein%20makes%20zero%20sense%2C%26quot%3B%20Matthew%20Hertz%2C%20founder%20of%20the%20third-party%20logistics%20platform%20Third%20Person%2C%20said%20to%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20wrote%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fhertz_tariffs-section321-deminimis-activity-7303128393913384960-yS-l%3Futm_source%3Dshare%26utm_medium%3Dmember_desktop%26rcm%3DACoAAAtNuO4BwQhonnAjH8q