ld%20BI%20on%20Friday%20that%20the%20US%20government%20had%20suspended%20Ukrainian%20accounts%20in%20the%20Global%20Enhanced%20GEOINT%20Delivery%20program%2C%20or%20GEGD%2C%20a%20major%20government%20portal%20for%20sharing%20government-purchased%20imagery%20with%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaxar%20is%20contracted%20with%20the%20National%20Geospatial-Intelligence%20Agency%20(NGA)%20on%20the%20program.%20The%20NGA%20told%20BI%20that%20it%20had%20%26quot%3Btemporarily%20suspended%26quot%3B%20access%20%26quot%3Bin%20accordance%20with%20the%20Administration's%20directive%20on%20support%20to%20Ukraine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20change%20hinders%20Ukraine's%20awareness%20of%20the%20Russian%20forces%20behind%20the%20frontlines%20and%20obstructs%20their%20deep%20strike%20campaign%20that%20has%20targeted%20Russian%20supply%20lines%20and%20ammunition%20depots%2C%20said%20Dimko%20Zhluktenko%2C%20who%20works%20in%20Ukraine's%20Unmanned%20Systems%20Forces%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20move%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmil.in.ua%2Fen%2Fnews%2Fmaxar-cuts-off-ukraine-s-access-to-satellite-imagery%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20reported%20by%20Ukrainian%20outlet%20Militarnyi%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20unnamed%20sources%2C%20comes%20just%20after%20the%20US%20announced%20it%20was%20pausing%20its%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Ftrump-intelligence-sharing-russia-ukraine-nato-f8ed7e5e9d40b24ba3c075b80894ce5f%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20intelligence%20sharing%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Ukraine%20and%20days%20after%20President%20Donald%20Trump%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-pauses-military-aid-ukraine-weapons-zelenskyy-white-house-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20announced%20an%20indefinite%20pause%20in%20US%20aid%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Ukraine%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-weapons-europe-replace-us-tech-ukraine-himars-patriots-abrams-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20leaving%20the%20future%20of%20a%20major%20weapons%20source%20in%20doubt%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20like%20Starlink%2C%20the%20SpaceX%20internet%20satellite%20service%20provided%20to%20Ukraine%20through%20US%20government%20contracts%2C%20commercial%20satellite%20images%20are%20essential%20to%20the%20planning%20and%20execution%20of%20Ukraine's%20military%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZhluktenko%20said%20that%20Ukraine's%20Unmanned%20Systems%20Forces%2C%20a%20branch%20that%20specializes%20in%20drone%20operations%2C%20relies%20more%20heavily%20on%20satellite%20imagery%20from%20private%20companies%20like%20Maxar%20than%20it%20does%20on%20intelligence%20given%20directly%20by%20the%20US%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithout%20Maxar%20imagery%2C%20%26quot%3Bdeepstrike%20drone%20operators%20will%20not%20get%20as%20precise%20targeting%2C%26quot%3B%20Zhluktenko%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIntelligence%20services%20will%20have%20worse%20understanding%20of%20Russian%20stockpiles%20and%20repair%20factories%26quot%3B%20and%20have%20%26quot%3Ba%20worse%20understanding%20of%20how%20much%20capacity%20Russia%20has%20left.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20his%20unit%20often%20used%20Maxar%20satellite%20imagery%20to%20plan%20reconnaissance%20drone%20missions%2C%20to%20find%20deep%20strike%20targets%20and%20places%20where%20Russia%20was%20storing%20equipment%20like%20tanks%20and%20vehicles%2C%20and%20to%20see%20the%20results%20of%20those%20deep%20strikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Maxar%20satellite%20imagery%20showing%20a%20Russian%20fortifications%2C%20including%20dragon's%20teeth%20and%20trenches%2C%20along%20a%20coastline.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6488cb3662d3f10019968438%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20satellite%20image%20by%20Maxar%20shows%20Russian%20military%20obstacles%20and%20trenches%20in%20Crimea.%3Cp%3EMaxar%20Technologies%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EZhluktenko%20said%20Ukrainian%20soldiers%20use%20a%20mix%20of%20different%20satellite%20imagery%20companies%2C%20but%20that%20Maxar%20stood%20out%20because%20of%20the%20quality%20of%20its%20images.%20He%20estimated%20that%2075%25%20of%20the%20units%20that%20use%20drone%20imagery%20largely%20rely%20on%20Maxar%20specifically%20because%20%26quot%3Bhigh-quality%20satellite%20images%20and%20maps%20are%20a%20must.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20its%20assistance%20to%20Ukraine%2C%20the%20company's%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbefore-after-satellite-images-ukraine-wipe-out-russian-ammo-depots-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0images%20have%20widely%20documented%20the%20changes%20and%20damage%20occurring%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrones%20have%20become%20an%20increasingly%20important%20part%20of%20Ukraine's%20fight%20back%20against%20Russia's%20invasion.%20Ukraine%20can%20make%20drones%20itself%2C%20whereas%20its%20supply%20of%20Western%20aid%2C%20while%20large%2C%20has%20often%20come%20with%20conditions%20or%20delays%20and%20has%20an%20unclear%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAcross%20the%20600-mile%20stretch%20of%20the%20frontlines%2C%20drones%20have%20taken%20on%20the%20roles%20of%20anti-tank%20missiles%20and%20other%20weaponry.%20Even%20cheap%20drones%20have%20hit%20far%20behind%20Russia's%20lines%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvideo-cheap-ukraine-drone-destroys-10m-russia-air-defense-system-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20destroyed%20pieces%20of%20equipment%20worth%20millions%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20contributed%20strongly%20to%20Ukraine%20holding%20Russia%20back.%20The%20USF%2C%20set%20up%20in%202024%2C%20is%20considered%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-setting-up-separate-military-branch-focused-drone-warfare-russia-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20world's%20first%20military%20branch%20devoted%20solely%20to%20drone%20warfare%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20drone%20units%20as%20of%20%3Cs%3Elast%3C%2Fs%3E%20November%20accounted%20for%20at%20least%2080%25%20of%20Russian%20frontline%20losses%2C%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20then%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F11%2F20%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussia-ukraine-war-attacks-trump.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20weakening%20Ukraine's%20drones%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20at%20the%20same%20time%20that%20aid%20from%20the%20US%20is%20paused%20%E2%80%94%20could%20have%20a%20major%20impact%20on%20the%20battlefield.%20This%20effect%20gets%20more%20pronounced%20as%20the%20imagery%20stoppage%20continues%2C%20allowing%20Russia%20to%20mass%20forces%20for%20assault%20with%20a%20lower%20chance%20of%20being%20spotted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Ukrainian%20drone%20units%20have%20become%20increasingly%20reliant%20on%20satellite%20imagery%20as%20a%20way%20to%20get%20around%20Russian%20jamming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ukraine's%20drone%20pilots%20rely%20on%20high-resolute%20satellite%20imagery%20to%20navigate%20in%20the%20many%20areas%20where%20GPS%20navigation%20signals%20are%20disrupted.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67cb419669253ccddf98a181%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUkraine's%20drone%20pilots%20rely%20on%20high-resolute%20satellite%20imagery%20to%20navigate%20in%20the%20many%20areas%20where%20GPS%20navigation%20signals%20are%20disrupted.%3Cp%3EMiguel%20Candela%2FSOPA%20Images%2FLightRocket%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EZhluktenko%20said%20that%20using%20GPS%20is%20impossible%20in%20heavily%20contested%20areas%20as%20jamming%20efforts%20are%20so%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20place%20of%20locating%20with%20GPS%2C%20drone%20operators%20increasingly%20orient%20themselves%20by%20comparing%20the%20drone%20camera's%20view%20to%20maps%20and%20satellite%20images%2C%20Zhluktenko%20said.%20In%20this%20way%2C%20Maxar%20technology%20helps%20them%20%26quot%3Bnavigate%20the%20battlefield.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-special-forces-drone-tech-no-gps-russia-cant-jam-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20has%20been%20developing%20drones%20that%20work%20along%20these%20lines%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cu%3E%20%3C%2Fu%3E%E2%80%94%20with%20software%20that%20compares%20what%20the%20drone%20sees%20to%20photos%20and%20video%20of%20the%20area%20that%20was%20previously%20captured%20%E2%80%94%20to%20get%20around%20Russian%20jamming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmerican%20company%20Vermeer%20announced%20last%20month%20that%20it%20was%20integrating%20its%20technology%20into%20Ukrainian%20drones.%20This%20technology%20preloads%20satellite%20images%20onto%20drones%20so%20they%20don't%20need%20to%20rely%20on%20GPS.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EZhlutenko%20said%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20actions%20are%20making%20Ukraine%20weaker%20and%20could%20be%20used%20against%20other%20US%20allies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20the%20NGA%20awarded%20Maxar%20a%20five-year%2C%20%24192%20million%20contract%20which%20would%20help%20provide%20US%20allies%20with%20imagery%20%26quot%3Bconsisting%20of%20high-resolution%20electro-optical%2C%20synthetic%20aperture%20radar%20(SAR)%20and%203D%20data%20products%2C%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.maxar.com%2Fpress-releases%2Fmaxar-awarded-192m-foreign-commercial-imagery-program-idiq-contract%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20the%20company%20announced%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump-ordered%20intelligence%20freeze%20may%20have%20most%20immediate%20impact%20by%20limiting%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20Ukraine's%20air%20defenses%2C%20which%20a