20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMexico%20City%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20saw%20more%20of%20the%20property%2C%20I%20passed%20a%20spa%2C%20multiple%20restaurants%2C%20and%20different%20pool%20types.%20Overall%2C%20I%20found%20the%20rooms%20and%20amenities%20felt%20higher%20quality%20and%20more%20diversified%20than%20I'd%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b773cae8-0d3c-4959-97ab-804acad9f534%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlthough%20once%20a%20buffet%20naysayer%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20pleasantly%20surprised%20by%20the%20food%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20skeptical%20about%20the%20food%2C%20assuming%20it%20would%20all%20be%20buffet-style%20and%20sacrifice%20quantity%20over%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20opinion%2C%20it's%20rare%20for%20a%20buffet%20to%20truly%20offer%20a%20wonderful%20culinary%20experience.%20In%20many%20cases%2C%20diners%20might%20leave%20a%20buffet%20uncomfortably%20full%2C%20only%20convincing%20themselves%20it%20was%20good%20because%20they%20got%20their%20money's%20worth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20much%20to%20my%20surprise%2C%20my%20favorite%20meal%20at%20the%20property%20was%20at%20a%20daily%20buffet%2C%20where%20I%20tried%20a%20bit%20of%20everything%3A%20chilaquiles%2C%20huevos%20rancheros%2C%20pan%20dulce%2C%20fruit%2C%20and%20even%20Americanized%20lunch%20staples%20such%20as%20chicken%20fajitas.%20I%20even%20had%20a%20second%20helping.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20also%20pleased%20to%20find%20that%20most%20of%20the%20restaurants%20on%20the%20property%20operated%20like%20regular%20food%20establishments%20with%20menus%20and%20servers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20my%20first%20day%2C%20I%20had%20a%20particularly%20attentive%20server%20who%20noticed%20right%20away%20that%20I%20wasn't%20fully%20enjoying%20my%20lunch%20and%20offered%20to%20bring%20me%20a%20different%20dish.%20That%20level%20of%20service%20impressed%20me.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20I%20had%20expected%20gimmicky%20buffets%20and%20subpar-quality%20food%2C%20the%20dining%20experience%20at%20the%20resort%20didn't%20let%20me%20down.%20None%20of%20the%20dishes%20I%20ate%20were%20bad%2C%20even%20if%20a%20lot%20of%20them%20weren't%20particularly%20memorable.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f74d1057-5792-4afa-a778-d120659d0e4a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOverall%2C%20it%20felt%20nice%20to%20run%20around%20liberated%20from%20tabs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224592%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A.%20waterfall%20in%20Mexico%20flowing%20into%20turquoise%20waters%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b5f6d6eb4be2fff9a4fcb0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223056%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20liked%20that%20we%20were%20able%20to%20leave%20the%20property%20and%20visit%20other%20areas%20in%20Mexico%20if%20we%20wanted.%20%3Cp%3Ewww.infinitahighway.com.br%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20I%20was%20worried%20about%20trading%20my%20free%20will%20for%20prepaid%20perimeters%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20enjoying%20the%20all-inclusive%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20watched%20guests%20bar%20hopping%2C%20pool%20hopping%2C%20and%20flagging%20down%20golf%20carts%20to%20take%20them%20from%20one%20spot%20to%20the%20next%20(even%20though%20everything%20was%20walkable)%2C%20I%20started%20to%20understand%20the%20appeal%20I'd%20doubted.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20resort%20wasn't%20just%20designed%20to%20be%20a%20place%20to%20stay%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20a%20grand%20experience%20all%20on%20its%20own.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20all%2C%20I%20loved%20walking%20around%20without%20my%20wallet.%20The%20ease%20of%20switching%20from%20one%20restaurant%20to%20the%20next%20at%20a%20moment's%20notice%20without%20needing%20to%20request%20any%20checks%20made%20me%20feel%20as%20if%20I%20owned%20the%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20way%2C%20being%20at%20an%20all-inclusive%20resort%20felt%20similar%20to%20being%20on%20a%20cruise.%20Plus%2C%20we%20didn't%20have%20to%20leave%20the%20grounds%20if%20we%20didn't%20want%20to.%20The%20adventurist%20in%20me%20hated%20the%20fact%20I%20thought%20that%20was%20a%20good%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20appreciated%20the%20convenience%20but%20also%20that%20we%20were%20able%20to%20leave%20the%20property%20and%20seek%20out%20some%20adventure%20by%20having%20private%20drivers%20take%20us%20to%20nearby%20volcanoes%20and%20waterfalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELastly%2C%20a%3Cspan%3Elthough%20I'd%20thought%20that%20%26quot%3Ball-inclusive%26quot%3B%20referred%20only%20to%20a%20type%20of%20midrange%20hotel%2C%20I%20learned%20that%20even%20high-end%20hotels%20offer%20the%20service.%20The%20W%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20my%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexperts-say-these-9-hotel-chains-are-ones-to-watch-2021-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efavorite%20hotel%20chains%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%94%20even%20offers%20all-inclusive%20dining%20and%20drinking%20packages%20at%20its%20location%20nearby.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20I%20didn't%20leave%20with%20the%20feeling%20that%20I%20%3Cem%3Emust%3C%2Fem%3E%20return%20to%20this%20exact%20resort%2C%20but%20I'd%20be%20willing%20to%20consider%20an%20all-inclusive%20option%20the%20next%20time%20it%20appears%20on%20the%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-people-like-all-inclusive-resorts-first-stay-mexico-skeptical-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741378921000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b5f7817bb3f854015d3ac5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-people-like-all-inclusive-resorts-first-stay-mexico-skeptical-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20never%20thought%20I'd%20enjoy%20staying%20at%20an%